cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM

This paper focuses on texture synthesis using deep generative feed-forward networks, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and graphics (cs.GR) research. The paper also introduces techniques for achieving better convergence and diversity, which are relevant to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper discusses the application of the proposed model for stylization, which falls under multimedia (cs.MM).
